<org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription xmi:version="2.0" xmlns:xmi="http://www.omg.org/XMI" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:org.eclipse.epf.uma="http://www.eclipse.org/epf/uma/1.0.6/uma.ecore" xmlns:rmc="http://www.ibm.com/rmc" rmc:version="7.5.1" xmlns:epf="http://www.eclipse.org/epf" epf:version="1.5.1" xmi:id="-nNenriVIlXpGF7MMW59ZDQ" name="refine_system_management_plan,mweb093C356700000113C11CAC4EEC5CB1DF" guid="-nNenriVIlXpGF7MMW59ZDQ" changeDate="2011-07-27T12:34:59.328-0700" version="1">
  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    Starting from the outline IT Services Strategy developed earlier, develop the plan into a detailed framework adequate&#xD;
    to ensure the system management related nonfunctional requirements can be met. Make a list of necessary hardware&#xD;
    platforms and software environments that are necessary to implement functionality of the systems. Utilize the Systems&#xD;
    Management Framework Design (SMFD) matrices for collection of all such information.&lt;br />&#xD;
    &lt;br />&#xD;
    Also, refine the Software Distribution Plan developed earlier, defining precisely what will be distributed where.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Correlate systems management functions to the Deployment Units, Non-functional Requirements, Operational Model,&#xD;
        network architecture, and Software Distribution Plan.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Systems management evaluation will typically require a database to catalog all the information, so that it can be&#xD;
        sorted and reports generated. Manual processing of all the data for a large enterprise with many elements can be&#xD;
        unmanageable.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></mainDescription>
  <externalId xsi:nil="true"/>
  <keyConsiderations xsi:nil="true"/>
  <purpose>The purpose of this task is to complete the systems management and software distribution plans.&lt;br />&#xD;
&lt;br />&#xD;
This provides the basis for the following: &#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        The selection of system management tools.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        The selection of systems management processes.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Selecting and defining job descriptions, based on identified roles, to support the IT system.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></purpose>
  <alternatives xsi:nil="true"/>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription>
